      "options": {
        "content": "## About This Dashboard\n\n**Project Hammer** is the Toronto Island Ferry Tracker — a real-time web app showing ferry departure schedules and dock status.\n\n| Component | Target | Infrastructure |\n|---|---|---|\n| Frontend SPA | ferries.yyz.live | AWS S3 + CloudFront |\n| Backend API | project-hammer-api.fly.dev/api/health | Fly.io (yyz region) |\n\nBoth endpoints are probed every 15 s via Blackbox Exporter (HTTP 2xx). Fly.io cold-start latency can spike to 2–3 s — the high-latency alert fires if response time exceeds 3 s for 5 minutes.\n\n*Onboarded by Helldiver Squadron Alpha*",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
